Study Finds Most Execs Aren’t Ready for GDPR Enforcement, but New Data Analyzer Tool Can Help
A May 2018 report by the IBM Institute for Business Value found that only 36 percent of surveyed executives believed they’d be fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) by the May 25 enforcement date.
