DevSecOps is maturing, 62% of organizations have a team in place
During RSA Conference 2018, Aqua Security surveyed 80 security professionals to gain their unfiltered, high-level perspective on the fast-emerging discipline of DevSecOps. According to the survey respondents, DevSecOps is quickly gaining support and traction, within and beyond information security teams.
