Open Source Tools for Active Defense Security
This term originates from the defense world and refers to techniques that deny positions or strategic resources to adversaries, which then makes their campaigns more challenging to conduct. In the cybersecurity world, the goal is the same: Make the adversaries’ campaigns harder by denying them key resources.
https://securityintelligence.com/open-source-tools-for-active-defense-security/
